  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">How We May Use and Disclose Other Information We Collect Similarly we generally use Other Information for any purpose not prohibited by law In particular we may collect compile store publish promote report sell or otherwise disclose or use any and all Other Information provided that such information does not personally identify you Other Information that we collect generally will not personally identify you or be correlated to you individually for external purposes</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

