  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Your California Privacy Rights If you live in California and have an established business relationship with us you can request a list of the personal information we have shared with third parties for their marketing purposes We will also give you a list of the third parties that have received your information You can make a request one time each year To exercise your rights you can contact us by email at online notmc com or as set forth in the Contact Us section below Please be sure to mention when you contact us that you are making a California Shine the Light inquiry We will respond within 30 days</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

